AbstractType<T> - Class in io.shiromi.saml.types
Instances of the class AbstractType represent a type value assignable to a YamlElement's value, each separate type has its own methods and implementation, however they can all be cast to GenericType as it has parameter <T> set to Object, therefore each subtype of this class can be cast to it.
AbstractType(T) - Constructor for class io.shiromi.saml.types.AbstractType
